  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees.",
    "Toast the bread slices until lightly browned.",
    "In a large bowl, mix together the cooked rice noodles, argentinian chimichurri sauce, smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Spread the noodle mixture evenly onto the toasted bread slices.",
    "Sprinkle the grated cheddar cheese over the noodle mixture.",
    "Place the bread slices under the broiler and cook until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Remove the bread slices from the oven and let cool for a few minutes.",
    "Cut the bread slices into halves or quarters and serve immediately."
